  "text": "The ten included studies owned 1,371 participants (737 PCa patients and 634 controls). Their characteristics and the numbers of TP, FP. FN, and TN with the corresponding SEN, SPE are listed in Table 1 . The number of included studies for miR-21 and miR-30c were, respectively, six and four. Countries of participants for miR-21 involved Poland, China, and Egypt, while miR-30c only involved China. Relative expressions of miR-21 in case group were higher than that in control group. On the contrary, relative expressions of miR-30c were lower in case group. Two studies assessed miR-30c from PCa cancer tissue and PCa adjacent normal tissue, 7, [CITATION_1] and other two studies assessed miR-30c from plasma of PCa patients and control group.",
